I made this recipe and tripled it. I also used my own mayo. I used just 3/4 cup mayo per batch but it was way too much. Next time i will use like 1/4-1/2 cup and add it gradually. The salad was fantastic. Also, a double stack was too much for my taste -- a normal single stack was easier.

