Rating: 4
This was a crowd pleaser. Interesting flavor and a little unusual, but very tasty. Because it's flavorful, I found that it tasted better with a rather thin layer of the filling, so that it wasn't too strong and you had the right ratio of bread to filling. Also, the boiled egg is a must. I also cut the mayo to 3/4 a cup with no problem.

